=== 客機型號 ===
此次失蹤的客機为[[波音777|波音777-2H6ER]]{{NoteTag|这架是一架波音777-200ER（Extended Range）型飞机。波音公司为每个购买飞机的公司分配一个[[波音公司客户代码列表|独特的客户代码]]，用[[中缀|中缀]]表示。马来西亚航空公司的代码是“H6”，因此也可以写作“波音777-2H6ER”。<ref>{{cite book |last= Pither |first= Tony |title = The Boeing 707 720 and C-135 |year= 1998 |publisher= [[Air-Britain|Air-Britain (Historians) Ltd]] |location=England |ISBN = 0-85130-236-X}}</ref>}}型长程双发动机宽体客机。该机于2002年5月14日首飛，同年5月31日交付給馬來西亞航空，使用[[劳斯莱斯瑞达#特倫特800|劳斯莱斯瑞达892型]]引擎，座艙佈局包括35個商務艙座位和247個經濟艙座位{{rs |date = 2013年3月}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.planespotters.net/Production_List/Boeing/777/28420,9M-MRO-Malaysia-Airlines.php |title=9M-MRO Malaysia Airlines Boeing 777-2H6(ER) - cn 28420 / ln 404 |publisher=Planespotters.net |accessdate=2014-03-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308074436/http://www.planespotters.net/Production_List/Boeing/777/28420,9M-MRO-Malaysia-Airlines.php |archivedate=2014-03-08 }}</ref>。據航空公司，該飛機已累計飛行3023次，共20243小時<ref>{{cite news| title = Boeing 777 at centre of Malaysia Airlines disappearance had clocked up 'normal' 20,000 hours' flying time |publisher = South China Morning Post |accessdate = 2014-03-08 |url = http://www.scmp.com/news/asia/article/1443524/lost-malaysia-airlines-plane-had-clocked-normal-20000-hours-flying-time |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title = Contact lost with Malaysian 777 |publisher = Australian Aviation |date = 2014-03-08 |url = http://australianaviation.com.au/2014/03/contact-lost-with-malaysian-777/ |language=en}}</ref>。

